<emphasis bold="true" box="[2076,2252,1634,1667]" pageId="202" pageNumber="480">Distribution.</emphasis>
Known from a few localities in Cordoba and San Luis provinces, NC 
<taxonomicName box="[2076,2220,1717,1746]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rosaceae" genus="Argentina" kingdom="Plantae" order="Rosales" pageId="202" pageNumber="480" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">Argentina</taxonomicName>
